9 Amend the resolve by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or
10 section number to read consecutively.
11 SUMMARY
1122 This amendment requires the Department of Health and Human Services, instead of
1133 contracting with an independent service provider as in the resolve, to amend an existing
1144 contract with the Youth Leadership Advisory Team at the University of Southern Maine to
1155 evaluate mentoring program options for youth with extended care and support agreements
1166 with the department. The amendment adds an appropriations and allocations section.
